text: Gao Xin and Zhang Zhizhen were the defending champions but lost in the quarterfinals to Gong Maoxin and Zhang Ze. Gong and Zhang Ze won the title after Bradley Mousley and Akira Santillan withdrew before the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw International Challenger Zhangjiagang - Doubles 2018 Doubles
